name: Cayuga
absentee_method: Merged into voters' home precincts AFTER election night
nyt_race_description_race: Democrats are eager to unseat the Republican incumbent, John Katko, in this Syracuse-based district that Hillary Clinton won in 2016. Dana Balter, an activist who teaches at Syracuse University, lost to Mr. Katko by five points in 2018.
